How to install FFV-C package
============================

1) Choose an applicable install script.

  install_intel.sh  <=  Intel compiler
  install_gnu.sh    <=  GNU compiler
  install_fx.sh     <=  FUJITSU compiler


2) Edit build parameters.

  FFV_HOME = Install directory, default directory is ~/FFV
  TMP_LDFLAGS = Directory path for fortran libraries

In case of the GNU compiler, you may need to specify TMP_LDFLAGS, that includes
fortran library.


3) Type a command.

# single precision
$ ./install_*.sh

# double precision
$ ./install_*.sh double


The executable modules are installed at the specified directory.
